id":"Vdz3amarRsGwW89wmPUg2g","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"3. Acidosis metabolica: pH menor de 7.3, HCO3 menor de 18, anion gap mayor de 12","guid":"YtMILKsNTKiGSV_pwBpsjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"82","text":"Clasificacion\\Nseveridad DKA","guid":"B-mIPFOyT4CH_YYD6gihCQ","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Leve: pH 7.25-7.30, HCO3 15-18, BHB 3-6, alerta","guid":"64ZZ_UYwR_SZ5LxlN7w0Zg","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"Moderada: pH 7.0-7.25, HCO3 10-15, BHB 3-6, alerta/somnoliento","guid":"ZUCUvkONSiO7h6t2ezCl1w","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"Severa: pH menor de 7.0, HCO3 menor de 10, BHB mayor de 6, estupor/coma → UCI","guid":"YNy_vS9PS2mfpoyo8Y7wlw","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"82","text":"Criterios HHS\\N(4 criterios)","guid":"ko4ncIhcS12Zdghcx12zPw","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"1. Glicemia mayor de 600 mg/dL","guid":"RIxxRw_nSLOQ_SRBaTSCpw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"2. Osmolaridad efectiva mayor de 320 mOsm/kg","guid":"Y72huYxdRnezvOV09E8N7Q","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"3. Deshidratacion clinica","guid":"1f1Ouf5ASxSIWTB1MN8gSQ","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"4. Sin cetonemia severa ni acidosis (pH 7.3 o mayor, HCO3 18 o mayor)","guid":"EbprepLVSBCRmQh9GCyOpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"82","text":"DKA EUGLICEMICA\\N(glicemia menor de 200 mg/dL)","guid":"vDj-TrORQHSf-fNi32IQ-g","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Causas: insulina exogena, inanicion, embarazo, alcoholismo, iSGLT2","guid":"oN9CPyrHSeaKhVbPVCO0Cw","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"SUSPENDER iSGLT2 ante sospecha","guid":"tnpAOyL2RDWz7NDfqq5v3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"82","text":"Evaluacion\\Ninicial","guid":"442MPOOxTBGH_KS2Sk6VQQ","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Glicemia, electrolitos, GSV, hemograma, cetonas sangre/orina","guid":"pxfQGOWZRIupnJtRce45Ww","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"ECG (ondas T picudas → hiperkalemia)","guid":"jJejfWxLTTmjbbHbBKcnCg","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"Buscar precipitante: infeccion, isquemia","guid":"CPdSNDyqTfGPaikXr4qfiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"82","text":"DKA: horas a pocos dias / HHS: dias a semanas de evolucion","guid":"j2zjZ5uIQSaNs6xceo9_TA","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"82","text":"Superposicion DKA-HHS en ~30% casos","guid":"IN_duUS2SWelGOwA_h_F9w","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"sQornLwkTHCIkx48731BNw","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Principios generales","guid":"6Ow1DSaESpC6dPidhaE6qQ","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Fluidos IV + insulina + electrolitos + tratar precipitante","guid":"ZwKS8DECSAiVW9BjpxjQ1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Monitorizacion","guid":"ClCvj3AOR-aYyB6G9_Kp4Q","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Glicemia capilar cada 1-2h","guid":"HUXBi83SRPWqAyfV0ZdHaA","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Electrolitos, creatinina, BHB, pH venoso cada 4h","guid":"0fOSj3WkRWWiJ0tmsY6ttw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"Osmolaridad serica cada 4h (HHS)","guid":"9yk0mrRJS-q3N9WpNJfHyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"105","text":"Terapia\\Nde fluidos","guid":"XY0jGAoiR52dGg4j7CY8zg","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Inicio: SF 0.9% o cristaloides balanceados","guid":"dSxNt9-7SFK0Y1G-liLztg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"Tasa inicial 500-1000 mL/h primeras 2-4h","guid":"ighNYtfRTuy5tF-VAsDxSQ","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"ADULTOS MAYORES FRAGILES: bolos 250 mL + evaluacion hemodinamica frecuente","guid":"mPXii2lhRAqCVsK0lHAVSw","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"IC, ERC: precaucion sobrecarga","guid":"IDE_cmElSKi5gLei7ycAoA","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"Cristaloides balanceados (RL, Plasmalyte) → resolucion mas rapida acidosis vs SF 0.9%","guid":"bgKYvGN9Tn-9xbhdCJbCMA","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"112","text":"SF 0.9% causa acidosis hipercloremica → confunde interpretacion","guid":"DS6_5bwoSCONA7Oe-KKIFw","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"112","text":"DKA: agregar dextrosa 5-10% cuando glicemia menor de 250 mg/dL","guid":"YvFILZGCT_2N2sLzDZ-TPg","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"112","text":"HHS: descenso glicemia no mayor de 90-120 mg/dL/h → evitar edema cerebral","guid":"anKkQ6v0RiGU4gsKc5K7FQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"105","text":"Terapia de\\Ninsulina en DKA","guid":"5wkJc03JTa-BVM_xYBvcog","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Infusion IV continua tasa fija 0.1 U/kg/h","guid":"MwW5ZpHiSNCzcOWkHsj3Fg","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Alternativa sin bolo: 0.14 U/kg/h (Kitabchi: bolo NO mejora outcomes)","guid":"zbEVDPibTkSsOWjr59ISbQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"Bolo inicial opcional 0.1 U/kg IV/IM si retraso acceso venoso","guid":"8fy0smPaSFaJFltzEsNbhQ","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"Glicemia 250 mg/dL → agregar dextrosa + reducir a 0.05 U/kg/h","guid":"R_fXRethTgu_OsCmgyKMJg","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"Mantener ~200 mg/dL hasta resolver cetoacidosis","guid":"xdBcG4D1T_S2xkrgbqBJ7A","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"121","text":"DKA leve/moderada: alternativa SC rapida cada 1-2h (sin UCI)","guid":"d7dpYQzKQeKJH2BXpIP90Q","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"121","text":"GLARGINA TEMPRANA\\N(primeras 3h)","guid":"CTCHjUquTrCaxsXZN_OEog","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Resolucion mas rapida (9.89 vs 12.73h, p=0.022)","guid":"SESSr9TkRHKo6ZyL14qWCw","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Menor estancia (4.75 vs 15.25 dias, p=0.024)","guid":"yAi92H1OQ_SGzjYMGHW0nA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Sin aumento hipoglicemia","guid":"is0qQjsiQ6KuzeQhLtc90g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"105","text":"Terapia de\\Ninsulina en HHS","guid":"KU8njwHmRJesWGe3xDnHXQ","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Sin cetosis: infusion IV 0.05 U/kg/h","guid":"RdAPNeGeSzulkZ92zbFDeQ","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"Cetosis significativa (mixto): 0.1 U/kg/h","guid":"MlSHkcrJT9eoVnM5x5KcnQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"Continuar insulina basal ajustada","guid":"oa3Bj-pCTjexmYmG5Z-qIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"105","text":"Transicion\\Ninsulina IV\\Na SC","guid":"aNK_JbDOTd6nATEyEoBPqg","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Superponer 1-2h insulina SC antes de suspender IV","guid":"82_r0O6pSXmWyCqvDDtrNw","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"Paciente conocido: dosis preadmision","guid":"MKyvzgQfTMy653FckCHSUg","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"Insulin-naive: 0.5-0.6 U/kg/dia TDD","guid":"8lFpEG9TSpuDCZtFuNGRMQ","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"Fragil/ERC: ~0.3 U/kg/dia TDD","guid":"g8DF4bk7SXK39ZaeEZG-bw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"136","text":"Basal 0.15-0.3 U/kg SC 1-2 veces/dia","guid":"F_e4Dv2ST-i86uL0IovZSw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"136","text":"Regimen basal-bolo al alta SIEMPRE","guid":"ngBap_zDQcqdVVZJQ4sjBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"105","text":"Potasio\\N(CRITICO)","guid":"exbDRjeiQaav7de8ZPQc6A","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Deficit corporal total: 300-600 mEq","guid":"Fd7pZiXURUy4QdTeoOZkhQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"K+ serico normal/alto por acidosis + deficit insulina","guid":"AMxcqltoS5exdSQW7H5OZw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"Reponer cuando K menor de 5.0 mmol/L: 20-30 mmol/L fluido IV","guid":"OdVWZS7AQ_G4rJSh4WBXxQ","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"K menor de 3.5 mmol/L: 10 mmol/h + DETENER INSULINA hasta K mayor de 3.5","guid":"bmCZdtzgRyiw9sRV3_h1BQ","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"Hipokalemia severa (2.5 o menor): mortalidad 3 VECES MAYOR","guid":"MU_gF5irRjK2-v-gzhDgGQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"143","text":"Descenso tipico 1-2 mmol/L en primeras 48h","guid":"Nxj73UypTcGLxOF3RX-MRw","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"143","text":"Monitorizar K+ 2h post-inicio insulina, luego cada 4h","guid":"n4cVVkDxQom8klI8OxbVHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"105","text":"Bicarbonato","guid":"b70SzCEOTRm8ZITP5Dxwqg","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"NO recomendado rutinariamente","guid":"CJQzr9bZTKiPGJtytelVhw","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"Sin ventaja en outcomes cardiacos/neurologicos","guid":"WaGjiiLuRKuOwhFJPPfqaQ","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"Riesgos: hipokalemia, edema cerebral, acidosis paradojica SNC","guid":"Jddo-zSXQuyHTDCENSfXXg","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"151","text":"Considerar si pH menor de 7.0: NaHCO3 100 mmol en 400 mL cada 2h","guid":"aPTfuyPfSQqOVL_RNbuknw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"151","text":"PERI-INTUBACION: considerar si pH menor de 7.2 o HCO3 menor de 10 (buffer apnea)","guid":"aVKRxYxVSd2X49GyODibcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"105","text":"Fosfato","guid":"s9jBhS7MTJ-uL6sTrfzopA","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"No reposicion rutinaria","guid":"NLe3VClfQCmDUijpkNPSgw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Solo si menor de 1.0 mmol/L con debilidad muscular/respiratoria","guid":"WcEozeh5S_aQB-PP5Gj5kw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Dosis: 20-30 mmol K-fosfato en fluidos","guid":"BW_B-qFWTemPYw-mQFFosA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"Reposicion rapida → precipita hipocalcemia","guid":"aYbYT6UjRAOk9uX2zuwW8g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Criterios de\\Nresolucion","guid":"VvXrJG7CQamVw3K3RVbjVA","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"DKA resuelta","guid":"wYnm2MDtRrql1S300QtP2w","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"BHB menor de 0.6 mmol/L","guid":"Y2Tb9QBESZS05fxuxS1cRw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"pH venoso 7.3 o mayor","guid":"dZOal02GQx2Dgh_Kbp7Qcg","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"HCO3 18 o mayor","guid":"rSJfxq2uQ3ixq1PZ81XT8Q","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"Glicemia menor de 200 mg/dL","guid":"pawSWD0rQAO78UG6IS9s1Q","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"163","text":"NO usar anion gap (acidosis hipercloremica post-tratamiento)","guid":"LXBvyqATRueBKRPqRl05cQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"162","text":"HHS resuelta","guid":"Vk9jC2GcRRe_nOXnJmV8fA","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Osmolaridad menor de 300 mOsm/kg","guid":"FLfipVA4SSqnCpvLL9HF2Q","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"Diuresis mayor de 0.5 mL/kg/h","guid":"tfYtADcgQIGwoXmdA2ZxVQ","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"Estado cognitivo premorbido recuperado","guid":"oOOh5N0OTW6fgiOxccYmnQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"Glicemia menor de 250 mg/dL","guid":"ckzBtGS8T-CzgLVSNPfuJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"162","text":"Guia JBDS 2022: osmolaridad 2xNa + glucosa + urea mayor de 320 → HHS","guid":"aRKa_waGRKOjbm7dOEqiig","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones del\\Ntratamiento","guid":"9n43orVOTOC6IghkWmvuFQ","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Hipoglicemia → monitoreo frecuente + dextrosa cuando glicemia menor de 250","guid":"whLLXE-0RKezhoTI_AM_RQ","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"Hipokalemia → reposicion K+ cada 2-4h","guid":"VZ_0SdGhTY-z0fZJsnZdXQ","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"Acidosis metabolica AG normal → por exceso SF 0.9% → preferir balanceados","guid":"IlP-apLQTa2RxZ08MS8RgA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"Trombosis → hidratacion + profilaxis antitrombotica en alto riesgo","guid":"n3B-kTtaTDOl57Zs7zad2g","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"Edema cerebral","guid":"2NzN5NW6ThCdfrOvqjtEqw","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Descenso rapido osmolaridad (mayor de 3-8 mOsm/kg/h)","guid":"JFswwIG0Ty2RGFPeHp099Q","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"Mortalidad 20-40%","guid":"ku0wPvp4RXGZMjRfBA5B4A","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"NO SOLO PEDIATRICO → tambien adultos","guid":"otVrI0AoRHqxJLSRDQ0fiA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"Si Na no sube mientras glicemia baja → sospechar","guid":"kLjdFLSlQX-ZHYFb66tMpg","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"175","text":"Sindrome desmielinizacion osmotica","guid":"lCS95q-iTnaoT8hI4St6nA","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Correccion rapida hipernatremia","guid":"X5fWdKJmQiKgaU5Ys1_l3Q","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"No exceder descenso Na mayor de 10 mmol/L en 24h","guid":"nRaeXiItTjuxiqKzTFnmng","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"175","text":"Lesion renal aguda → hidratacion + evitar nefrotoxicos","guid":"1DwmGXOGSmelQ_5b46GAOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"0","text":"Poblaciones\\Nespeciales","guid":"GD3HmnrkQiatZuzigs1U4A","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"ADULTO MAYOR FRAGIL","guid":"X-O6XV2ESya85mfXrv-2Ug","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"Mayor riesgo hipoglicemia y sobrecarga fluidos","guid":"msgfCqO9SUm5eP8otocE7w","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"Comorbilidades multiples (IC, ERC, deterioro cognitivo)","guid":"wb7psEGDQ0S_YCpUMD2ecw","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"Dosis iniciales mas bajas insulina y fluidos (250 mL bolos)","guid":"ceYoSVM-Q5KIxVzEOssVmQ","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"Ajustes lentos y cuidadosos","guid":"j6SHtBBSTpuLJa9udTRKAQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"190","text":"Monitoreo frecuente estado hemodinamico","guid":"6QVkGxoVR669zKEzcsSDFA","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"190","text":"TDD insulina ~0.3 U/kg/dia (factor fragilidad/ERC)","guid":"6n5t9jtURmaPTSw5eY5l3Q","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"190","text":"HHS MAS COMUN → deshidratacion cronica + baja ingesta","guid":"XgDl-UTfSPySAQS8wreydA","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"189","text":"Inhibidores SGLT2","guid":"jMTcOtVPRr-VOefc4grD_Q","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"Riesgo DKA euglicemica → SUSPENDER ante sospecha","guid":"-4tXn5XITI6pFMo4YPeNtg","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"Monitorizar cetonas en sangre","guid":"z9YUMgzqRiy-l2qUv2SmDA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"Reiniciar solo cuando resuelto y con supervision","guid":"uDp2JaWUSn6cipdx71hkJA","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"NO iniciar ni continuar durante hospitalizacion","guid":"lZr7UNeYTQqENHzOIYBheQ","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"No usar en DM1 ni DM2 propensa a cetosis","guid":"KD6bPHqAStK_zQIoFW2haw","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"189","text":"Enfermedad renal terminal","guid":"SPn4L4ELSoicmbFqfJPegA","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"Riesgo hiperkalemia y sobrecarga volumen","guid":"YWLR4s3rS8y-MGkynBzkgA","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"Bolos 250 mL IV","guid":"c-RSsdF0SEGCuYA_jKMMTg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"Coordinacion con nefrologia","guid":"ULMdaTqKRlWRsQKjqTuwBA","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"Monitoreo frecuente electrolitos","guid":"o6tmwvP-SkKA1XVpEpx5KQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"189","text":"Insuficiencia cardiaca","guid":"kN7tHXBPSZSRzTgCwx8IFw","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"DKA + IC: aOR mortalidad 2.75, shock cardiogenico aOR 2.53","guid":"p7aYv_XSQSSERko3dswUIQ","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"Fluidos cautelosos, monitoreo hemodinamico estricto","guid":"es4kvsLYSDa-CJvE9nzYdQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"0","text":"Manejo via aerea en DKA (UCI)","guid":"twc1PSQGQV2-lP9_nAyTcg","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"Evitar BiPAP (riesgo aspiracion)","guid":"DeHdllIiSnWzJkFEY2aXXw","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Intubacion: controversial por demanda ventilatoria alta (Kussmaul)","guid":"4b1Ovfx6RvG712FHkaL_sg","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"Post-intubacion: VM alto (TV 6-8 mL/kg, FR hasta 32)","guid":"SUzvSWxdRx-oEeO9Mn-HxA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"212","text":"GSA cada 15-30 min post-intubacion","guid":"boRjYfBrTuetDowppPemgw","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"212","text":"Succinilcolina preferida (corta duracion) → segura si K menor de 5.5","guid":"OLdR3GgCTxSRvv7o4KVibg","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"212","text":"Rocuronio si hiperkalemia severa","guid":"7GTgutKMQ6mmaClWwfmrnA","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"212","text":"Bicarbonato peri-intubacion si pH menor de 7.2 → buffer durante apnea","guid":"6br5PRALRwea3FtxCUqe0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"0","text":"Nutricion en DKA","guid":"x9Qo9A6iQZiDd5aHbAIcww","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"Nutricion temprana (menor de 24h) es SEGURA (Lipatov et al.)","guid":"MYaUe2WKSuijOxMIB3avAg","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"Reduce estancia UCI y hospitalaria","guid":"dPVR3nb2RC21NqDafRt68A","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"220","text":"Disminuye hipokalemia e hipofosfatemia","guid":"0U3Dmr5GQOKmk3_DhCh6aw","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"220","text":"Sin diferencias en mortalidad o hipoglicemia","guid":"PVaie2Q5TbSfo1OvL2K1Rw","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"220","text":"NO dejar NPO hasta pH normal","guid":"4eTTT3tTTUCz4RC388XwTA","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"0","text":"Prevencion","guid":"PEhDQzVwQlO89hiYxGhqAg","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"Seguimiento 2-4 semanas post-alta","guid":"nW5XFBWDQuKjRGtjj1obLg","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"Hasta 22% reingreso en 30 dias (50% dentro de 2 semanas)","guid":"lC7qQtKWShiNu_ev4P72hA","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"226","text":"Evaluacion salud mental al ingreso y alta","guid":"Tw7iYmHuSYK7vpIDNyPH0Q","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"Depresion, trastornos alimentarios, esquizofrenia","guid":"CLgRS1fwSN2kT7mRUoCt3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"226","text":"Determinantes sociales: bajos ingresos, red apoyo, acceso insulina","guid":"tY8M0Z6MQ0OiWZ_Znjr-Zw","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"226","text":"Educacion estructurada del paciente","guid":"oHe8rb82RbaBdaX9UxaUOQ","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"Tecnica inyeccion, monitoreo glicemia, pruebas cetonas","guid":"e9CUxbLnSDujbNNKNZkiZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"226","text":"CGM recomendado por ADA-EASD","guid":"90r6gym0R8Gdw0y4QgLQ5g","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"Francia: reduccion 53% hospitalizaciones DKA en DM1, 47% en DM2","guid":"J0et0VoMTQe2gksh7ZTxhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"226","text":"Telemedicina y servicio emergencia 24h","guid":"C1ZINUJ5R_qBQCd8kW7j1Q","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"226","text":"Intervenciones psicologicas, apoyo pares, coaching","guid":"eVMSImrYS7amDvHJFCalcQ","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"226","text":"Racionamiento insulina hasta 20% → mayor riesgo DKA","guid":"2V8278NDR_GRVAvhSr74eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"U2_PcldvTB-stMI2iF_tVA","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"STOP POTASIO: si K menor de 3.3 → PROHIBIDO iniciar insulina (riesgo paro)","guid":"OKpvnV5aQBGE3_v2VioPEA","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"239","text":"Cristaloides balanceados mayor que SF 0.9% → resolucion acidosis mas rapida, evita confusion interpretacion","guid":"DKcaTBXjTcWli95stxF_lg","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"239","text":"Glargina temprana (3h) junto a bomba IV → resolucion mas rapida sin aumento hipoglicemia","guid":"uu8cAcZIS4ikr-XmJYPNSw","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"239","text":"Bolo insulina NO necesario si infusion continua adecuada (0.14 U/kg/h)","guid":"8WpC3QtRQBu7ON-lviiCgg","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"239","text":"En AM fragil: bolos 250 mL + TDD ~0.3 U/kg + monitoreo estricto","guid":"N0Y-hjqlTRu2w3PM0H8BEQ","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"239","text":"HHS es MAS COMUN en AM → deshidratacion cronica + baja ingesta oral","guid":"zx3viW4CR8WTW1bjS8pxSA","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"239","text":"DKA euglicemica: siempre considerar iSGLT2 → suspender inmediatamente","guid":"2Z9mlSmjTHieykTUu8eZCg","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"239","text":"Edema cerebral NO es exclusivo pediatrico → si Na no sube mientras glicemia baja, sospechar","guid":"aJOawcGcR0KicZ1ug4XF2A","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"239","text":"Peri-intubacion: bicarbonato como buffer si pH menor de 7.2 + VM con FR alta (28-32)","guid":"1p-klYlqS2mGt6xqi79AcQ","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"239","text":"Nutricion temprana (menor de 24h) es segura y reduce complicaciones electroliticas","guid":"aQq8z_LpQ-af8ekCDyzE8g","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"239","text":"NO usar anion gap como criterio resolucion DKA (acidosis hipercloremica confunde)","guid":"lg7whk2FQMO1Yi9fC_6OcQ","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"239","text":"DKA + IC: mortalidad aOR 2.75 → manejo fluidos cauteloso es critico","guid":"os3AMlg3RTyA00kv1f9E9A","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"239","text":"Monitorizar K+ a las 2h de iniciar insulina → descenso rapido esperable","guid":"699mRjTRTJmhSVntttzxOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"EMELOr8LRi6jqteikHJLfQ","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"1. Umpierrez GE, et al. Hyperglycemic crises in adult patients with diabetes. Diabetes Care. 2024;47(Suppl1):S181-S198.","guid":"CxI70TyTSJa_iuglVqWL5Q","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"2. Dunn BK, et al. Treatment challenges in DKA in ICU. Cureus. 2024;16(9):e68785. DOI:10.7759/cureus.68785.","guid":"c3pFhzpeTl6q3lOUq7Yl1w","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"253","text":"3. Mustafa OG, et al. Management of HHS: updated JBDS guideline. Diabet Med. 2023;40(3):e15005. DOI:10.1111/dme.15005.","guid":"Cnvtm_nKQS-jKb8CmX8Bfw","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"253","text":"4. Alroobi H, et al. DKA and HHS in diabetes with heart failure. BMC Cardiovasc Disord. 2025;25(1):384. DOI:10.1186/s12872-025-04832-3.","guid":"cxB43odJRPedTM35MySAvw","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"253","text":"5. Kitabchi AE, et al. Hyperglycemic crises in adult patients with diabetes. Diabetes Care. 2009;32(7):1335-43.","guid":"eweVIzZDQ9CoqjXoQFEYrA","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"253","text":"6. Thammakosol K, Sriphrapradang C. Early glargine in DKA. J Endocr Soc. 2023.","guid":"eaMxyF3QTAWR1sCt7WUlAA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"253","text":"7. Lipatov K, et al. Early nutrition in DKA. Crit Care Med. 2023.","guid":"T0WHRgwPRUGjXL-AoGyfPg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":260,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Endocrinología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Endocrinología","filename":"Crisis Hiperglicemicas 2024","id":"map_545","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Crisis Hiperglicemicas 2024"}